      <h2>Our Story</h2>
      <p>FoodShare was founded in 2023 with a simple but powerful vision: to create a world where no good food goes to waste while people go hungry.</p>
      <p>We saw a disconnect in our communities - restaurants, stores, and individuals often had surplus food that would end up in landfills, while many people struggled to put meals on their tables. Our platform bridges this gap by connecting food donors directly with individuals and organizations that can put this food to good use.</p>
      <p>What started as a small local initiative has grown into a community of passionate donors and grateful receivers, all working together to reduce food waste and address food insecurity.</p>
    </div>
