      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>At FoodShare, we're committed to these core principles:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Reduce Food Waste:</strong> Approximately one-third of all food produced globally is wasted. We're working to change that by ensuring surplus food reaches those who need it instead of landfills.</li>
        <li><strong>Fight Food Insecurity:</strong> Millions of people worldwide don't have reliable access to affordable, nutritious food. Our platform helps address this crisis at the community level.</li>
        <li><strong>Build Community Connection:</strong> We believe in the power of neighbors helping neighbors. Our platform fosters direct connections between food donors and recipients.</li>
        <li><strong>Environmental Responsibility:</strong> Food waste is a major contributor to greenhouse gas emissions. By reducing waste, we're also helping combat climate change.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
