      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <p>Our platform is designed to be simple, efficient, and effective:</p>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Donors list food:</strong> Restaurants, grocery stores, event venues, and individuals can quickly list their surplus food, including details about quantity, pickup times, and expiration.</li>
        <li><strong>Receivers find food:</strong> Individuals, families, and community organizations in need can browse available food donations in their area.</li>
        <li><strong>Connection is made:</strong> Receivers request the food they need, and donors approve the requests.</li>
        <li><strong>Food is collected:</strong> Arrangements are made for pickup, reducing the logistical burden on both parties.</li>
        <li><strong>Community impact:</strong> Less food waste, less hunger, stronger communities, and a healthier planet.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
